---
title: Creamy Chicken à la Normande with Apples and Spring Green Colcannon
description: This delicious Creamy Chicken à la Normande has been expertly designed by our chefs as a lighter option to help with a balanced lifestyle. Cooking "à la Normande" means "in the style of Normandy", resulting in a creamy sauce with tart apples and a hint of sharp sweetness.
